<h3 style="margin-left: 1rem; margin-right: 1rem;">Heritage Hall Archives</h3>

<p class="alert alert-danger">Generally open 9:00am to 4:30pm, but hours can fluctuate.</p>

<p>Heritage Hall is the official archive of the Calvin University, Calvin Theological Seminary, and the Christian Reformed Church.</p>

<p>It also has some 600 collections of personal papers and records of other organizations.</p>

<p>It specializes in Dutch North American history and Reformed Christianity and offers rich material for genealogical research and topics in social, cultural, and political history.</p>

<hr>
